Once the Main Page user story is succesfull, the user will now be shown all events related to his interest in the geographical area he chose. 
It then can filter if he wants to be shown maybe some music or sporting events. There wwill be checklist option to fliter this at the top of the page. 
One can add events to a list of favorites and store them in his profile, which once again is linked directly to twitter. 
The client will be alt to click at the event and this will direct the User directy to Ticketmaster page so it can be able to purchase tickets. 
